(7369, 559, 'about-journey-content', '<h6>Armefin.com was started with a mission to help Two sets of Investors.</h6>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>DIY Investors</li>\r\n<li>Investors needing guidance</li>\r\n<p class=\"para\">With Armefin, we are addressing the issues by providing the platforms for Investment in Indian Stocks, Mutual Funds & Bonds for DIY Investors.</p>\r\n<p class=\"para\">For Investors needing support for higher capital amounts, we dig through the universe of Investment funds and managed account services and present 3-4 solutions to choose from with the reasoning, track record and risks involved. Saving time for the Investor to research about the investments.</p>\r\n<p class=\"para\">Process to get started is half the battle won in investment journey, we ensure the process is done correctly for onboarding our clients at the earliest and starting their money multiplying journey.</p>\r\n<p class=\"para\">At Armefin, We believe Equity investments should be part of a strategy to create & multiply your wealth over the long term. Equity investment, through publicly listed stocks or start-ups is one way to bet on people who are smarter than us and having the ability to strategise and execute growth plans at bigger scale. Simply putting it, how else can Ambanis or Tatas of India work for you to grow your money.</p>\r\n</ul>'),
(7370, 559, '_about-journey-content', 'field_650bf4536ef6c'),
(7371, 559, 'about-journey-img', '247'),
(7372, 559, '_about-journey-img', 'field_650c09c45d8dd'),
(7373, 559, 'about-funding-content', '<h2>Our Next Step: Funding Solutions</h2>\r\n<p>After 2020, the rise of interest in Indian Start-Ups has given rise to Private equity as an investment opportunity to many investors.</p>\r\n<p class=\"para\">Many of our clients had asked us to evaluate the investment opportunities that they were coming across in the private equity space. Coming from a team who have research background, we used strict due dilligence measures to evaluate the opportunities and provide our qualified opinion to our clients.</p>\r\n<p class=\"para\">As we already had investors interested in this asset class, we built our own Investment banking team to source potential start-up ideas and help them connect with Investors across the globe for scaling up and making money for the investors.</p>\r\n<p class=\"para\">During this phase, we came across established companies which are in business for more than 5 years and making positive cashflows, but needed capital to expand their business to the next level, we started helping them by connecting with Banks, NBFCs and AIF for private credit opportunities. This made our funding solutions more useful for Entreprenuers.</p>'),
(7374, 559, '_about-funding-content', 'field_650c0ae07c4e6'),
(7375, 559, 'about-team-content', '<h2>Our Team</h2>\r\n<p class=\"para\">Our team is led by Veteran Bankers and Investment professionals, supported by Investment associates and Research Analysts who like to interact with businesses to get the right information and present the most suitable opportunities to our clients for making their investment journey successful.</p>'),
