(9149, 644, '_fixclusive-repeater_1_fixclusive-img', 'field_651fa39074579'),
(9150, 644, 'fixclusive-repeater_1_fixclusive-cntnt', '<h4>EQUITY </h4>\r\n<p>Equity raises capital by selling shares of the business. There is no obligation to make regular repayments like debt funding, however a percentage of the business will belong to another party and the level of business control and decision making an owner has may be affected.</p>'),
(9151, 644, '_fixclusive-repeater_1_fixclusive-cntnt', 'field_651fa3a17457a'),
(9152, 644, 'fixclusive-repeater_2_fixclusive-img', '633'),
(9153, 644, '_fixclusive-repeater_2_fixclusive-img', 'field_651fa39074579'),
(9154, 644, 'fixclusive-repeater_2_fixclusive-cntnt', '<h4>MEZZANINE</h4>\r\n<p>Mezzanine finance (also referred to as a hybrid) combine elements of debt and equity to form an agile alternative to its counterparts, using equity as a form of business collateral often allowing for higher levels of capital received compared to solely debt lending.</p>'),
(9155, 644, '_fixclusive-repeater_2_fixclusive-cntnt', 'field_651fa3a17457a'),
(9156, 644, 'fixclusive-repeater', '3'),
(9157, 644, '_fixclusive-repeater', 'field_651fa36674578'),
(9158, 644, 'advantages-debt', '<h2>Advantages of Debt Funding</h2>\r\n<h5>Owners keep business control</h5>\r\n<p>A major advantage of securing debt funding is that you do not need to give up stakes in the business in order to receive capital. Unlike equity finance, decision making and business control remains undiluted, giving the comfort that the current management team is still 100% in control.</p>\r\n<h5>Flexible repayment plans</h5>\r\n<p>With repayments and interest set out in advance, a business can monitor cashflows and plan for future growth. You will know how much is needed to be paid back each month thereby supporting better budgeting and planning.</p>\r\n<h5>Flexible opportunities</h5>\r\n<p>Long-term debt can be used for a multitude of business purposes from MBOs, to shareholder transaction, from property developments to growth capital. Every business strategy is different and finding the right type of funding and right partner is essential to fulfilling business growth plans.</p>'),
(9159, 644, '_advantages-debt', 'field_651fa71b940c1'),
(9160, 644, 'advantages-debt-img', '638'),
