(9468, 138, 'buy-sell-content', '<h2>Mergers and acquisitions course curriculum</h2>\r\n<p>In a class on mergers and acquisitions, students can expect to delve into various aspects of these complex business activities. The course may cover the following key topics:</p>\r\n<p>Fundamental concepts of M&A, including definitions, types of transactions, and motivations</p>\r\n<p>Different approaches to valuing companies</p>\r\n<p>Various deal structures, including stock acquisitions, asset acquisitions, and mergers of equals</p>\r\n<p>Importance of conducting thorough due diligence</p>\r\n<p>Legal frameworks and regulations governing M&A transactions</p>'),
