(9496, 677, 'buy-sell-content', '<h2>Mergers and acquisitions course curriculum</h2>\r\n<p>In a class on mergers and acquisitions, students can expect to delve into various aspects of these complex business activities. The course may cover the following key topics:</p>\r\n<p>Fundamental concepts of M&A, including definitions, types of transactions, and motivations</p>\r\n<p>Different approaches to valuing companies</p>\r\n<p>Various deal structures, including stock acquisitions, asset acquisitions, and mergers of equals</p>\r\n<p>Importance of conducting thorough due diligence</p>\r\n<p>Legal frameworks and regulations governing M&A transactions</p>'),
(9497, 677, '_buy-sell-content', 'field_651fca8e6f1d7'),
(9498, 677, 'about-funding', '<h2>Explore jobs related to mergers and acquisitions</h2>\r\n<p>Learning about mergers and acquisitions can lead to various exciting and rewarding career opportunities in the field of finance, corporate strategy, and business development. Some potential career paths for individuals with expertise in mergers and acquisitions might include:</p>\r\n<p class=\"para\">Many of our clients had asked us to evaluate the investment opportunities that they were coming across in the private equity space. Coming from a team who have research background, we used strict due dilligence measures to evaluate the opportunities and provide our qualified opinion to our clients.</p>\r\n<p class=\"para\">As we already had investors interested in this asset class, we built our own Investment banking team to source potential start-up ideas and help them connect with Investors across the globe for scaling up and making money for the investors.</p>\r\n<p class=\"para\">During this phase, we came across established companies which are in business for more than 5 years and making positive cashflows, but needed capital to expand their business to the next level, we started helping them by connecting with Banks, NBFCs and AIF for private credit opportunities. This made our funding solutions more useful for Entreprenuers.</p>'),
