(9574, 698, 'alternative-content', '<h2>Get a federal tax ID</h2>\r\n<p>Getting an employer identification number (EIN) is necessary for most businesses to file taxes, open bank accounts and perform other essential tasks. The online application only takes a few minutes. </p>\r\n<p class=\"color\">How to Apply for an Employer Identification Number</p>\r\n<p class=\"color\">Benefits of Getting an EIN (Even If You Don’t Have To)</p>'),
