(12031, 936, 'wealth-repeater_1_wealth-demat-cntnt', '<h2>Mergers And Acquisitions</h2>\r\n<p>Mergers and acquisitions (M&amp;A) refer to the processes of combining two or more companies to form a new entity (merger) or one company acquiring another (acquisition). These strategic business activities aim to achieve various objectives, such as expanding market share, gaining new capabilities, accessing new markets, or achieving economies of scale. M&amp;A deals involve significant financial, legal, and operational considerations. They can have a profound impact on the involved organizations and their stakeholders.</p>'),
