(14551, 1068, 'what-demat-txt', '<h2>Investment Funds</h2>\r\n<p>We offer a selected range of investment funds through our Partners focused on Indian Equity Markets & Alternative Investments for the diversification of investor portfolios.</p>\r\n<h2>Indian Equity Funds</h2>\r\n <p>Investment Funds focused on Indian Public Listed Stocks and managed by Professional Fund managers regulated by the Securities & Exchange Board of India (SEBI) offering Index beating profits in USD & INR.</p>\r\n<p><line>INR Equity funds</line> are mainly CAT 3 AIFs closed-ended funds registered under SEBI with a minimum lock-in period of 3 Years and a minimum capital investment of INR 1 Crore.</p>\r\n<p><line>USD Equity funds</line> are Off-shore investment opportunities from Singapore, Mauritius & GIFT City(India) managed by Registered FPIs with a minimum investment of USD 100K and are mostly Open-ended funds without lock-in.</p>'),
