(14961, 1098, 'faq-repeater_1_faq-content', 'As per RBI guidelines, an NRI is allowed to have a maximum of one PIS from a designated bank. The PIS approval is linked with an NRE/ NRO account reckoning on their repatriation requirements. Hence, NRIs can have just one NRE PIS account and NRO PIS account. In case of NRO mode of transactions, PIS approval need not to be taken.'),
