(15029, 1100, 'debt-funding-txt', '<h2><span>Managed Accounts  </span> </h2>\r\n<p>Investment portfolios of the clients are expertly managed by registered professionals regulated by SEBI and other global authorities. While we don’t directly manage the accounts, we diligently research and identify the best professionals to handle your investments.</p>\r\n<p>Our primary focus is to provide personalized investment strategies that align with your specific financial goals and risk tolerance. Our dedicated team of investment professionals works tirelessly to ensure that your portfolio is tailored to your unique needs.</p>\r\n<p>By opting for our managed accounts solutions, you can enjoy a hassle-free investment experience. You can confidently delegate the day-to-day management and decision-making responsibilities to the experienced financial advisor while retaining full visibility and control over your investment portfolio.</p>'),
(15030, 1100, '_debt-funding-txt', 'field_652e5653fe9b2'),
(15031, 1100, 'usd-funds-repeater_0_usd-funds-txt', 'USD Account'),
(15032, 1100, '_usd-funds-repeater_0_usd-funds-txt', 'field_652e5b34c6b38'),
(15033, 1100, 'usd-funds-repeater_0_usd-funds-content', '<p class=\"pb-3\"><strong>Minimum Investment: US$ 1 Million</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"pb-3\">Our USD account solution is designed to cater to clients who prefer to invest in U.S. dollar-denominated assets. It provides the convenience of managing investments in one of the world’s leading currencies, allowing clients to access a wide range of investment opportunities and diversify their holdings beyond their local currency.</p>                 <p>This offering is mainly from Financial advisors registered under Singapore’s MAF, UAE’s DFSA & ADGM. The advisors have a proven track record of delivering extraordinary returns and have expertise in managing the accounts of billionaires of the world.</p>'),
(15034, 1100, '_usd-funds-repeater_0_usd-funds-content', 'field_652e5b52c6b39'),
