(15043, 1100, 'usd-funds-repeater_1_usd-funds-content', '<p class=\"pb-3\"><strong>Minimum Investment: INR 50 Lakhs (INR Five Million)</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"pb-3\">The INR account offers Indian & NRI clients the opportunity to invest in Indian rupee-denominated assets, tapping into the potential of the Indian economy. It provides access to diverse investment instruments, including equities, bonds, and more, while benefiting from the manager’s expertise in managing INR-denominated assets.</p>\r\n<p >This is known as Portfolio Management Services and is offered by Top Asset Managers in India like ASK group, Abakkus, ICICI Pru, and many registered entities under SEBI. The PMS service usually have a lock-in of 1 Year.</p>'),
