(15657, 1110, 'demat-content', '<h2>Business Setup Consulting</h2>\r\n<p>What business should you start? It depends on your expertise, plus how much time and money you’re able to invest. Some small-business ideas can be launched from home. </p>\r\n<p>If you’re not sure what kind of business you want to run, use these lists to get the wheels turning:</p>\r\n<p>Let’s jump into everything you need to know about crowdfunding for business: What it is, how to run successful crowdfunding campaigns, and every must-know crowdfunding site out there today for businesses.</p>\r\n<p class=\"color\">50 Best Small-Business Ideas</p>\r\n<p class=\"color\">The 23 Most Profitable Business Ideas</p>\r\n<p class=\"color\">Home Business Ideas: 40 Remote Jobs to Explore</p>\r\n<p class=\"color\">44 Online Business Ideas You Can Start Now</p>'),
