(17020, 1204, 'over-bg-txt1', '<h3>Conclusion</h3>\r\n<p>The Rangoli India Fund is poised to outperform due to its strategic focus on high-quality, growth-oriented businesses, its exposure to the key drivers of India’s economic growth, and its disciplined adherence to critical valuation metrics. This unique approach allows the fund to capitalize on the diverse opportunities in the Indian equity market, potentially delivering superior long-term returns.</p>'),
